{"title_page": "Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam Futsal Club", "text_new": "{{One source|date=September 2019}}\n{{Infobox football club\n| nickname = \n| ground   = Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam Stadium\n| capacity = 2,500\n| clubname = Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam FC\n| image    = \n| fullname = Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam Qu\u1eadn 8 Futsal Club \n| founded  = 2001\n| chairman = Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa\n| coach = Ph\u1ea1m Minh Giang\n| league   = [[Vietnam National Futsal League]]\n| season   = 2019 \n| position = 1st\n| current  =  \n| pattern_la1     = _whiteborder\n| pattern_la2     = _blueborder\n| pattern_b1         = _puma_white_horizontal_whith_v_neck| pattern_b2      = _arsenal9799a\n| pattern_ra1     = _whiteborder\n| pattern_ra2     = _blueborder\n| pattern_sh1     = \n| pattern_sh2     = \n| pattern_so1     = _2whitestripes\n| pattern_so2     = _bluestripe\n| leftarm1        = 2D2DFF\n| leftarm2        = FFFFFF\n| body1           = 2D2DFF\n| body2           = FFFFFF\n| rightarm1       = 2D2DFF\n| rightarm2       = FFFFFF\n| shorts1         = 2D2DFF\n| shorts2         = FFFFFF\n| socks1          = 2D2DFF\n| socks2          = FFFFFF\n}}\n\n'''Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam Futsal Club''' ([[Vietnamese language|Vietnamese]]: ''CLB Futsal Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam'') is a [[Vietnam]] [[futsal]] club. The team is current champion of [[Vietnam National Futsal League]] and is the most successful futsal club in Vietnam.\n\nTh\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam FC is also the one of the strongest teams in [[Asia]], having reaching [[AFC Futsal Club Championship]] final in [[2018 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2018]], and three bronze medals in [[2015 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2015]], [[2017 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2017]] and [[2019 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2019]].\n\n==Honours==\n\n===League===\n\n*'''[[Vietnam National Futsal League]]'''\n**'''[[File:Simple cup icon.svg]] Winners (7): 2010, 2013, 2014, 2016, 2017, 2018, 2019'''\n**'''{{SilverMedal}} Runners-up (2): 2011, 2012'''\n**'''{{BronzeMedal}} Third place (1): 2015'''\n\n===Cup===\n\n*'''[[Vietnamese National Futsal Cup]] '''\n**'''[[File:Simple cup icon.svg]] Champions (3): 2016, 2017, 2018'''\n\n*'''[[Ho Chi Minh City Futsal Cup]]'''\n**'''[[File:Simple cup icon.svg]] Champions (4): 2015, 2017, 2018, 2019'''\n**'''{{SilverMedal}} Runners-up (1): 2014'''\n**'''{{BronzeMedal}} Third place (1): 2016'''\n\n===International===\n\n*'''[[AFC Futsal Club Championship]]'''\n**'''{{SilverMedal}} Runner-up (1): 2018'''\n**'''{{BronzeMedal}} Third place (3): 2015, 2017, 2019'''\n\n*'''[[AFF Futsal Club Championship]]'''\n**'''{{SilverMedal}} Runner-up (1): 2016'''\n\n==[[AFC Futsal Club Championship|AFC Championship]] appearances==\n* {{flagicon|KUW}}  [[2012 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2012]] &mdash; Group stage\n* {{flagicon|JPN}} [[2013 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2013]] &mdash; Group stage  \n* {{flagicon|IRN}} [[2015 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2015]] &mdash; {{BronzeMedal}} '''Third place'''\n* {{flagicon|VIE}} [[2017 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2017]] &mdash; {{BronzeMedal}} '''Third place'''\n* {{flagicon|IDN}} [[2018 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2018]] &mdash; {{SilverMedal}} '''Runner-up'''\n* {{flagicon|THA}} [[2019 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2019]] &mdash; {{BronzeMedal}} '''Third place'''\n\n==International results==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!Season\n!Competition\n!Round\n!Country\n!Opponent\n!Result\n!Venue\n|-\n|rowspan=7 |[[2012 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2012]]\n|rowspan=7 align=center|AFC Futsal Club Championship\n|rowspan=4 |Preliminary Round \n|align=center|{{flagicon|AUS}}\n|[[Maccabi Hakoah Futsal Club|Maccabi Hakoah]]\n|style=\"background:#dfd;\"|1&ndash;0\n|[[Ho Chi Minh City]]\n|-\n|align=center|{{flagicon|CHN}}\n|[[Guangzhou Baiyunshan F.C|Guangzhou Baiyunshan]]\n|style=\"background:#dfd;\"|3&ndash;1\n|Ho Chi Minh City\n|-\n|align=center|{{flagicon|IDN}}\n|[[Pelindo Futsal Club|Pelindo FC]]\n|style=\"background:#dfd;\"|2&ndash;1\n|Ho Chi Minh City\n|-\n