p icon.svg]] Winners (7): 2010, 2013, 2014, 2016, 2017, 2018, 2019\n**'''{{SilverMedal}} Runners-up (2): 2011, 2012\n**'''{{BronzeMedal}} Third place (1): 2015\n\n===Cup===\n\n*'''[[Vietnamese National Futsal Cup]] '''\n**'''[[File:Simple cup icon.svg]] Champions (3): 2016, 2017, 2018\n\n*'''[[Ho Chi Minh City Futsal Cup]]'''\n**'''[[File:Simple cup icon.svg]] Champions (4): 2015, 2017, 2018, 2019\n**'''{{SilverMedal}} Runners-up (1): 2014\n**'''{{BronzeMedal}} Third place (1): 2016\n\n===International===\n\n*'''[[AFC Futsal Club Championship]]'''\n**'''{{SilverMedal}} Runner-up (1): 2018\n**'''{{BronzeMedal}} Third place (3): 2015, 2017, 2019\n\n*'''[[AFF Futsal Club Championship]]'''\n**'''{{SilverMedal}} Runner-up (1): 2016\n\n==[[AFC Futsal Club Championship|AFC Championship]] appearances==\n* {{flagicon|KUW}}  [[2012 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2012]] &mdash; Group stage\n* {{flagicon|JPN}} [[2013 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2013]] &mdash; Group stage  \n* {{flagicon|IRN}} [[2015 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2015]] &mdash; {{BronzeMedal}} '''Third place'''\n* {{flagicon|VIE}} [[2017 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2017]] &mdash; {{BronzeMedal}} '''Third place'''\n* {{flagicon|IDN}} [[2018 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2018]] &mdash; {{SilverMedal}} '''Runner-up'''\n* {{flagicon|THA}} [[2019 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2019]] &mdash; {{BronzeMedal}} '''Third place'''\n\n==International results==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!Season\n!Competition\n!Round\n!Country\n!Opponent\n!Result\n!Venue\n|-\n|rowspan=7 |[[2012 AFC Futsal Club Championship|2012]]\n|rowspan=7 align=center|AFC Futsal Club Championship\n|rowspan=4 |Preliminary Round \n|align=center|{{flagicon|AUS}}\n|[[Maccabi Hakoah Futsal Club|Maccabi Hakoah]]\n|style=\"background:#dfd;\"|1&ndash;0\n|[[Ho Chi Minh City]]\n|-\n|align=center|{{flagicon|CHN}}\n|[[Guangzhou Baiyunshan F.C|Guangzhou Baiyunshan]]\n|style=\"background:#dfd;\"|3&ndash;1\n|Ho Chi Minh City\n|-\n|align=center